Lord, we are ſo filled with joy and comfort, with delight and content, that we are not able to expreſs it here on Earth, and therefore take us to Heaven, that we may have that glory put upon us, that may inable us to declare and manifeſt thoſe glorious things that thou haſt wrought in us.

